# Mobile UX & App Shell

## Layout tokens (`globals.css`)
- `--lc-safe-top`, `--lc-safe-bottom`, `--lc-page-pad-bottom`
- Use `100dvh` over `100vh` for full-height panels
- `overflow-x: clip` on html/body/shell — avoid horizontal scroll bugs

## Fixed chrome
- **GlobalNav:** sticky top, safe-area-top, horizontal scroll tabs (no wrap), short labels ≤768px
- **LocaleSwitcher:** fixed bottom, safe-area insets, min 44px select
- **app-shell:** `appMain` gets `padding-block-end: var(--lc-page-pad-bottom)` — do not duplicate per-page unless page-specific need

## Touch & motion
- Interactive targets ≥ 44×44px (`accessibility.module.css` helpers)
- Chat/forge panels on mobile: reserve space for bottom chrome (`calc(100dvh - 13rem)` pattern)
- `GDPRConsent`: keep inside `AnimatePresence` conditional; `aria-modal="true"`

## Do not
- Nest `<main>` inside Providers wrapper (pages own the landmark)
- Use `calc(100vh - 4rem)` for diagnosis shell — nav height is dynamic
